videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu's runner is too strong, but she grabs her own rebound and lays the ball in for her first basket.

videos.headline: Ionescu drops 12 points in quiet WNBA debut
videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu struggles with her shot but plays a nice floor game in her WNBA debut with the Liberty, an 87-71 loss to the Storm.
